pan class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I would like to prove a existential version of it:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">path_is_rtc</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">forall</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">reachable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nonempty</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Path</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">diamond_freedom</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">reachable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">reachable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">reachable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">d</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">reachable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">d</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">reachable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">repeat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">path_is_rtc</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">@</span><span class=\"n\">diamond_freedom_pe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Vx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">d</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">repeat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rewrite</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Nonempty</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">imp</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- here, I have b &lt;= c -&gt; G.Path a b -&gt; G.Path a c -&gt; G.Path b d -&gt; G.Path c d -&gt; Nonempty (G.reachable b c)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Is there a better way than 5 intro and 5 revert? I cannot curry/uncurry because that's only for types, nor can I and_imp.</p>",
